    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "honestly he's also a bit stubborn about it. he says it's been like this for an hour and it's just getting better, not worse. he's also been drinking a lot of tea and saying he just has \"travel fatigue.\" you're sure it's not just maybe some circulation issues from sitting on the plane for so long? would it be okay if we just gave him some aspirin and let him nap for a bit to see if he feels better in the morning?",
